* unit tests for the non-ifblock flow stuff 
* fuzzie, 06/06/04

DBG: OUTS "TEST: flow: 3 tests"

* test LOOP .. UNTL
SETV VA00 0
LOOP
 ADDV VA00 1
UNTL VA00 eq 3
DOIF VA00 eq 3
 DBG: OUTS "PASS"
ELSE
 DBG: OUTS "FAIL"
ENDI

* test REPS .. REPE
SETV VA00 0
REPS 4
 ADDV VA00 1
REPE
DOIF VA00 eq 4
 DBG: OUTS "PASS"
ELSE
 DBG: OUTS "FAIL"
ENDI

* test GSUB
SETV VA00 0
GSUB test
DOIF VA00 eq 1
 DBG: OUTS "PASS"
ELSE
 DBG: OUTS "FAIL"
ENDI

* for GSUB test
SUBR test
 SETV VA00 1
RETN
